### 晏3 | _(A/)n(3)_ [[aan3]]

$$
R
  日 + 6
U
  U+664F
F
  ==
  [[F2.70 晏]] ::日[旰]也晚也又安也::
  ==
W
  ====
  - [[Page~4 晏(3)]]
    ==
    - Evening, sunset;
    - a serene, clear, sky;
    - tardy, behindhand;
    - peaceful, gentle;
    - rich, full, said of furs;
    - a tiffin;
    - _(2)h(i/) (1)shan (a/)n(3)_
        [[hei2 san1 aan3 起身晏]]
        to rise late;
    - _sh(e/)ung(6) (a/)n(3)_
        [[soeng6 aan3 上晏]]
        forenoon;
    - _fan(3) (a/)n(3) k(a/)u(3)_
        [[fan3 aan3 gaau3 瞓晏覺]]
        to take a siesta;
    - _fong(3) (a/)n(3) hok(9)_
        [[fong3 aan3 hok6 放晏學]]
        recess in school;
    - _shik(9) (a/)n(3)_
        [[sik6 aan3 食晏]]
        to eat lunch;
    - _(a/)n(3) chau(3)_
        [[aan3 zau3 晏晝]]
        noon;
    - _ts(o\)(6) (a/)n(3)_
        [[zou6 aan3 做晏]]
        to get tiffin;
    - _k(o\)m(3)(a/)n(3)_
        [[gam3 aan3 咁晏]]
        so late!
    ==
  ====
C
  ==
  - Fan Wan entry: Corrected 旴 (dawn) to 旰 (late).
  - Williams' "tiffin": British for "lunch".
  - Williams' 上晏: Now rarely heard; 上晝 is more common.
  ==
E
  ====
  - 【晏】 (aan3):
    ++
    1. Late (in the day).
       ==
       - 三點咁晏 (saam1 dim2 gam3 aan3): "3 o'clock? that late?"
       - 晏得嚌 (aan3 dak1 zai6): "[That's] too late [in the day]."
       ==
    1. Lunch.
       ==
       - 食晏未 (sik6 aan3 mei5): "Eaten lunch yet?"
       ==
    ++
  - 【晏晝】 (aan3 zau3):
    ++
    1. Afternoon.
       ==
       - 晏晝有戲睇 (aan3 zau3 jau5 hei3 tai2): "There's [a] movie [to] watch [in the] afternoon."
       ==
    ++
  ====
  --
  Olden attestation for 晏 _(a/)n(3)_ [[aan3]] meaning "late":
  --
  ====
  - 《廣韻》:
    ==
    - [[B4.w432a0202 烏旰切 (:晏:)]] ::(:晚也又於諫切:)::
    - [[B4.w434a0201 (:烏澗切:) (:晏:)]] ::柔也天淸也(:又晚也:)又姓左傳齊有晏氏代爲大夫::
    ==
  - Kangxi:
    ==
    - [[(:晏:)]] ::(:《唐韻》烏㵎切《集韻》《韻會》《正韻》於諫切𠀤音曣:)[...]<` `>\
      (:又《玉篇》晚也\
      《儀禮士相見禮》問日之早晏\
      《淮南子天文訓》日至于桑野是謂晏食\
      《屈原離騷》及年歲之未晏兮:)[...]::
